				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><p><strong data-start="1085" data-end="1103">品牌價值 × 印刷美學</strong></p>
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1161">圓廣印刷不僅是印刷廠，更是品牌包裝顧問。<br data-start="1124" data-end="1127" />我們用結構設計與色彩控制，幫你把品牌理念轉化為可觸摸的質感體驗。</p>
<ul data-start="1163" data-end="1259">
<li data-start="1163" data-end="1192">
<p data-start="1165" data-end="1192">採用 <strong data-start="1171" data-end="1183">FSC 環保紙材</strong>，實踐永續印刷</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1193" data-end="1217">
<p data-start="1195" data-end="1217">提供 <strong data-start="1201" data-end="1215">高精度打樣與色差管理</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1218" data-end="1243">
<p data-start="1220" data-end="1243">一對一顧問諮詢，協助新創品牌快速落地</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1244" data-end="1259">
<p data-start="1246" data-end="1259">打樣快速、交期穩定</p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote data-start="1261" data-end="1307">
<p data-start="1263" data-end="1307"><a data-start="1263" data-end="1307" href="https://page.line.me/568lyext?openQrModal=true" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">立即諮詢包裝顧問 →</a></p>
</blockquote>
