					<span class="et_overlay et_pb_inline_icon" data-icon="E"></span>
				</a>
				</div><h3 class="et_pb_gallery_title">白牛皮紙袋彩色印刷</h3><p class="et_pb_gallery_caption">以牛皮紙袋作為永續品牌的實踐起點
選用環保紙材與簡潔設計，紙袋成為企業落實 ESG 與溝通理念的第一接觸點。紙袋設計客製化展示，品牌印象強化</p></div><div class="et_pb_gallery_item et_pb_grid_item et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_gallery_item_3_7"><div class="et_pb_gallery_image landscape">
					<a href="https://www.rtadv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aluminum-bag-9.jpg" title="銅板紙袋彩色印刷">
					<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="400" height="284" src="https://www.rtadv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aluminum-bag-9-400x284.jpg" alt="設計客製紙袋前，必須了解印刷方式、尺寸設定、材質選擇、設計規範與實用建議。" srcset="https://www.rtadv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aluminum-bag-9.jpg 479w, https://www.rtadv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/aluminum-bag-9-400x284.jpg 480w" sizes="(max-width:479px) 479px, 100vw" class="wp-image-33614" title="客製化包裝設計與印刷｜紙盒·紙袋·紙罐·貼紙｜圓廣創意印刷 52">
